headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Faded Vapid Tee For Veteran Players
content: Brand loyalty is a valuable commodity these days. As a reward for their continued allegiance, players who already claimed the Vapid Tee during a GTA Online event will receive a rare Faded Vapid Tee, free of charge. This is the kind of irreplaceable vintage that collectors pay top dollar for - cherish it accordingly.
